It seems more intuitive for "gl" to mean "git log", and perhaps that was the intent. In the line below, a grouping of "git log"-related aliases can be seen. "git push" seems out of place.

https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/blob/51772732f54f01522ad5720e8ed0ba16ca3147ae/plugins/git/git.plugin.zsh#L186-L202

